articles.title: 634 Indian athletes cleared for 2023 Asian Games — Full List - The Bridge
articles.description: India will be sending their largest ever contingent to the Asian Games, up from 572 athletes at the 2018 Asian Games.
articles.content:
The final list of 634 Indian athletes for the 19th Asian Games in Hangzhou, China from September 23, 2023 was released by the Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports (MYAS) on Friday.
